Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.88,0:22:06.64,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I still remember you;
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.64,0:22:09.10,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}the time we shared,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.10,0:22:11.69,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}the love you gave.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.69,0:22:16.65,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Though everything has changed,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.65,0:22:21.36,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}you push me to live on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.36,0:22:31.20,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}海よりも深い奥底から見守っている
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.20,0:22:36.79,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別れた未来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.42,0:22:44.43,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I still love you, even though I miss you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.43,0:22:53.35,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}永久に続く悲しみの夜の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.35,0:22:58.19,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}愛は生きる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.11,0:23:03.86,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I will be here for you, always and forever
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.86,0:23:10.12,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今もずっと願っているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.12,0:23:21.09,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}温かいこの闇の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.88,0:22:06.64,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我依然记得你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.64,0:22:09.10,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}记得我们共度的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.10,0:22:11.69,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}记得你给予我的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.69,0:22:16.65,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}尽管一切都已面目全非
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.65,0:22:21.36,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你仍是我活着的动力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.36,0:22:31.20,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自比海更深的幽穴深底
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.20,0:22:36.79,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}守护着各自分歧的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.42,0:22:44.43,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我依然爱着你  即使我只能思念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.43,0:22:53.35,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在通向永恒的哀恸深夜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.35,0:22:58.19,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}犹自有爱存在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.11,0:23:03.86,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我会为你守在这里  始终如一  直到永远
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.86,0:23:10.12,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我仍将继续为你祈愿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.12,0:23:21.09,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在这温暖的黑暗之中
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-Sign-
