Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.14,0:08:58.77,Caption_Cinema_10,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}趁现在将法普塔...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.81,0:13:14.27,Caption_Cinema_10,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}快看！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.92,0:21:12.79,Caption_Cinema_10,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}被发现了！
